description: 2013 BMW 528i — Alpine White exterior, Veneto Beige leather interior. It’s the car that politely reminds other sedans it’s not trying too hard — it just is. Highlights - Engine: 2.0L Turbocharged inline-4 producing a spirited 240 hp and 260 lb-ft of torque. Smooth, efficient, and quick on its feet. - Transmission: BMW’s slick 8-speed automatic for relaxed cruising and crisp downshifts when you decide to be playful. - Fuel economy: an easy-going 24 MPG city / 34 MPG highway — the kind of numbers your wallet secretly approves of. - Mileage: below 80,000 miles (averaging under 6,000 miles per year). This one was clearly a weekend enthusiast, not a daily commuter. - History: Clean CARFAX. No unpleasant surprises hiding in the trunk. Factory-equipped features (the good stuff the factory actually included) - Driving Dynamics Control: Choose Comfort for civilized commuting, Sport when you want a firmer feel, and Eco Pro to remind yourself you can be responsible and stylish simultaneously. - iDrive infotainment system with rotary controller and center display for audio, vehicle settings, and more — modern conveniences without a touch-screen argument. - Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming plus USB/AUX input for your playlists. - Dual-zone automatic climate control so driver and passenger can each be temperature monarchs. - Veneto Beige leather upholstery — soft, elegant, and far less likely to show coffee spills than you fear. - Power-adjustable front seats with lumbar support and memory settings so your ideal seating position is just a button away. - Multi-function steering wheel with audio and cruise controls for less reaching, more driving. - Power windows, power door locks, and heated power mirrors — the little luxuries that make mornings feel civilized. - Automatic headlights and washer-wiper conveniences, modern visibility features that don’t complain about rain. - Comprehensive safety suite: anti-lock brakes (ABS), Dynamic Stability Control (DSC), traction control, and full-length airbags for peace of mind that’s actually engineered. - Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) and a secure keyless entry/start setup for convenience. - Stylish exterior in Alpine White — crisp, clean, and very hard to ignore in a tasteful way. Condition This 528i is in excellent overall condition. The paint shines, the leather is well cared for, and the mechanicals are tidy — the sort of car that makes you want to roll down the windows and play something dramatic, but with good taste. If you’re looking for a luxury sedan that blends efficient turbocharged performance, refined BMW driving dynamics, and a polished interior, this Alpine White 2013 528i in Veneto Beige leather is a delightful choice. Want to see if it’s your next soulmate on wheels? description:
Introducing the 2013 Nissan Altima 2.5 SV - the perfect fusion of style, performance, and technology. This sleek sedan boasts a spacious interior and a powerful engine, making it the ultimate choice for those seeking a reliable and comfortable ride.

Step inside and experience the luxurious and spacious cabin, designed with premium materials and modern features. The Altima 2.5 SV offers ample legroom and headroom for both the driver and passengers, ensuring a comfortable ride for everyone. The well-crafted seats provide excellent support, making long drives a breeze.

Under the hood, you'll find a 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine that delivers a smooth and responsive performance. Paired with a continuously variable transmission (CVT), this engine produces 182 horsepower and achieves impressive fuel efficiency, making it ideal for both city and highway driving.

But the Altima 2.5 SV isn't just about performance, it's also packed with advanced technology to enhance your driving experience. The NissanConnect system offers a range of features, including hands-free calling, navigation, and music streaming, all easily accessible through the 7-inch touchscreen display.

Safety is also a top priority for the Altima 2.5 SV. It comes equipped with a comprehensive set of features such as blind-spot monitoring, rear cross-traffic alert, and forward-collision warning, to keep you and your passengers safe on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2013 Nissan Altima 2.5 SV. With its stylish design, impressive performance, and advanced technology, it's the perfect choice for anyone looking for a reliable and comfortable sedan. Come take a test drive and experience it for yourself today.

description:
This 2013 Honda Accord Sdn EX-L, has a White Orchid Pearl exterior and an Ivory interior color. 50,736 miles. Stock Number N25191. Contact our Internet Sales Manager at (775)337-9706. No Accidents! One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
  • Heated driver seatback - That's hot. Heated driver seatback provides more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower back pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in the heated driver seatback.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2013 Ford Taurus Limited, a sophisticated and well-equipped sedan that offers a refined driving experience. This meticulously maintained vehicle boasts a striking Gray exterior, complemented by a spacious and well-appointed interior that exudes comfort and style.

• Local Trade-In
• Leather Seats
• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• AM/FM Stereo/Single CD/MP3 Capable
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Front Dual Zone A/C
• Power Driver Seat
• Power Steering
• Power Windows
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• Equipment Group 300A

Powered by a robust 3.5L 6-Cylinder SMPI DOHC engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Taurus Limited delivers an impressive blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway. Its responsive handling and smooth ride quality make it a pleasure to drive, whether navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

The interior of the Taurus Limited is a true haven, featuring perforated leather-trimmed front bucket seats that provide exceptional comfort and support. Dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone on board can enjoy their ideal temperature, while the Rear Parking Sensors and Exterior Parking Camera Rear make parking a breeze. The comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, provides added peace of mind.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2013 Ford Taurus Limited. This exceptional sedan offers a winning combination of style, comfort, and advanced technology, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the exceptional qualities of this remarkable vehicle for yourself.

The 2013 Subaru Legacy 4dr Sdn H4 Auto 2.5i Sport is a striking vehicle that combines performance, style, and versatility. Its Ice Silver Metallic exterior presents a sleek, modern look, accentuated by the distinctive trunk lip spoiler, offering an aerodynamic edge. The Black Striated interior exudes sophistication, providing a comfortable and refined driving experience.Under the hood, the Legacy features a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, delivering ample power with impressive fuel efficiency. This model boasts an All-Wheel Drive drivetrain, ensuring stability and control across various terrains and weather conditions, a hallmark of Subaru engineering. The popular package 2 enhances convenience and functionality, making every journey a pleasure.Additional features include an auto-dimming mirror with compass and HomeLink, providing seamless connectivity and reduced glare for safer night driving. The splash guards subtly protect the exterior, while the rear bumper applique adds an extra layer of defense against scratches and dings. Tailored for those who appreciate style and substance, the 2013 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Sport perfectly balances performance with luxury. description:
Discover the epitome of modern sophistication and performance in this stunning 2013 Ford Fusion Titanium. This exceptional vehicle is poised to elevate your driving experience, offering a captivating blend of style, technology, and uncompromising capability.

Indulge in the premium features that set this Fusion Titanium apart:

• LEATHER SEATS
• SUNROOF MOONROOF
• DUAL POWER SEATS
• BLUE TOOTH
• TITANIUM DRIVER ASSIST PKG
• ADAPTIVE CRUISE CONTROL
• MOONROOF W/UNIVERSAL GARAGE DOOR OPENER
• ACTIVE PARK ASSIST W/FORWARD SENSING SYSTEM
• VOICE-ACTIVATED NAVIGATION SYSTEM
• 19" Y-SPOKE MACHINED ALUMINUM WHEELS W/PAINTED POCKETS

Powered by the responsive EcoBoost 2.0L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine, this Fusion Titanium delivers an exhilarating driving experience with an impressive 22 city/33 highway MPG. The 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel-drive configuration provide a seamless and efficient performance, ensuring you command the road with confidence.

Step inside this meticulously maintained Fusion Titanium and be captivated by the premium leather-trimmed heated sport bucket seats, which offer exceptional comfort and support. The SONY Premium Audio System with 12 speakers creates an immersive listening experience, while the voice-activated navigation system and Bluetooth connectivity keep you connected and in control.

Elevating your driving experience further, this Fusion Titanium is equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, including a blind spot monitor with cross-traffic alert, lane departure warning, lane keep assist, driver monitoring, and auto high beams. The adaptive cruise control and collision mitigation by braking provide an added layer of protection, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

Distinctive in its White Platinum Metallic Tri-Coat exterior, this Fusion Titanium commands attention wherever it goes. The 19-inch Y-spoke machined aluminum wheels with painted pockets add a touch of refined style, complementing the vehicle's sleek and modern design.

Discover the true essence of sophisticated driving in this 2013 Ford Fusion Titanium. Schedule a test drive today and experience the unparalleled blend of performance, technology, and luxury that this exceptional vehicle has to offer.

description:
Tonkin Value Car!!!

Recent Arrival! 2013 Toyota Camry

This 2013 Toyota Camry is a standout midsize sedan known for its reliability, comfort, and excellent fuel efficiency. With Toyotas reputation for long-term dependability, the Camry is a smart choice for commuters, families, and first-time buyers alike.

Inside, you'll find a comfortable cabin featuring cloth seating, front bucket seats, a split-folding rear seat, and a 6.1" touchscreen audio system with AM/FM/CD and steering wheel mounted controls. Thoughtful touches like power windows and locks, cruise control, and outside temperature display make everyday driving easy and enjoyable.

Safety is a strong focus with ABS, Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, brake assist, and a full complement of airbags including knee and rear side-impact airbags, providing confidence on every drive. The smooth ride is supported by four-wheel independent suspension, ensuring comfort on city streets and highways.

Recognized year after year for its value, this Camry earned multiple honors including KBBs 10 Best New Sedans Under $25,000, Best Resale Value, and Brand Image Awards, while delivering an efficient 25 MPG city/35 MPG highway.

Call 503-255-4100 and ask for the Sales Manager
Browse more quality vehicles at www.tonkinchevrolet.com

Introducing the 2013 Volkswagen Jetta, a powerful and reliable sedan that is sure to exceed your expectations. But that's not all, this Jetta also comes with a variety of features to enhance your driving experience. From its advanced safety features to its modern technology, this Jetta has it all. So why wait? Come in today and test drive this 2013 Volkswagen Jetta and experience the power, efficiency, and luxury for yourself. This 2024 GMC Sierra 1500 Denali is a true powerhouse, combining exceptional performance and premium features to deliver an unparalleled driving experience. Equipped with the robust EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine and a 10-speed automatic transmission, this Sierra delivers impressive power and efficiency, with a commanding 4-wheel-drive system that ensures confident handling in any condition.

The Denali trim level elevates this Sierra to new heights, with a host of premium amenities that cater to your every need. Sink into the plush, perforated leather-appointed seats, which are both heated and ventilated for year-round comfort. The heated steering wheel and dual-zone automatic climate control further enhance the luxurious cabin experience. Stay connected with the state-of-the-art GMC Infotainment System, featuring wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, as well as a Bose premium audio system to immerse you in your favorite tunes.

Designed with both form and function in mind, the Sierra 1500 Denali boasts a striking exterior with bold, distinctive styling cues. The signature Denali chrome grille, 22-inch painted aluminum wheels, and power-retractable assist steps add a touch of sophistication and presence to this impressive full-size truck.

But the true standout feature of this Sierra is the cutting-edge Super Cruise technology. With this advanced driver assistance system, you can experience semi-autonomous driving on compatible roads, allowing you to navigate with confidence and ease. The system's precision and responsiveness will forever change the way you think about long-distance driving.

2019 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon 4WD — Clean CARFAX, Best Price in Turlock, CA

Looking for a rugged, capable SUV with modern tech and proven off-road performance? This 2019 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon with a 2.0L Turbo 4-cylinder gasoline engine and 4WD delivers. Located in Turlock, CA, this Jeep Wrangler Rubicon combines legendary trail capability with commuter-friendly features and a CARFAX Clean Report for added peace of mind.

Key features include a back-up camera for safer parking and trailhead maneuvers, automatic climate control to keep the cabin comfortable year-round, and Apple CarPlay for seamless smartphone integration. description: Step into the driver's seat of this sleek Gray 2015 Subaru Legacy and feel the power of the 2.5L DOHC 16 Valve 4-Cylinder engine at your fingertips. Equipped with a Lineartronic Continuously Variable transmission and steering-wheel paddle-shift control switches, you'll experience a smooth and exhilarating ride every time you hit the road. The full-time all-wheel drive and brake-actuated limited slip differential provide exceptional traction and control, making each drive an adventure.Picture yourself cruising on the 17" aluminum alloy wheels, with a compact spare tire ready for any unexpected bumps along the way. Slip into the comfortable heated front bucket seats, with ten-way power adjustments for the driver, and enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic air conditioning. Stay connected with Aha Selective Service internet access and keep track of vehicle information through the user-configurable triple meter display.With features like the rear-vision camera and rear cross-traffic alert, you'll always feel secure behind the wheel. Plus, rest assured knowing that a Carfax report is available for this vehicle, giving you peace of mind about its history. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this well-equipped Subaru Legacy yours! Visit Tacony Imports Inc dba Mayfair Auto Sales to shop our great deals. You can call 215-613-7065 to schedule your test drive today.

description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2015 Honda Accord Sport! This premium sedan offers a perfect blend of performance, comfort, and technology. With its spacious interior and advanced features, the Accord Sport is the perfect vehicle for both your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 2.4-liter four-cylinder engine, delivering a smooth and efficient ride. The Accord Sport also boasts a sport-tuned suspension and dual exhaust, providing an exhilarating driving experience. Plus, with its eco-friendly design, you can go further with fewer stops at the pump.

Step inside and experience the luxurious interior of the Accord Sport. The spacious cabin offers plenty of legroom and headroom for all passengers, making it perfect for long drives. The leather-trimmed seats and heated front seats add an extra touch of comfort and elegance.

The 2015 Honda Accord Sport also comes equipped with advanced technology features, including a 7-inch touchscreen display, Bluetooth connectivity, and a rearview camera. Stay connected and entertained while on the road with the Accord Sport's impressive technology features.

Safety is a top priority for Honda, and the Accord Sport is no exception. With its advanced safety features such as Lane Keep Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Forward Collision Warning, you can drive with peace of mind knowing your vehicle has your back.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2015 Honda Accord Sport. With its sleek design, powerful performance, and advanced features, it's the perfect sedan for anyone looking for a top-of-the-line driving experience. Visit our showroom today and take the Accord Sport for a test drive. You won't be disappointed!

description:
Experience the thrill of the open road with this stunning 2015 Kia Optima SX Turbo. This meticulously maintained vehicle boasts a sleek silver exterior and a host of premium features that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Packed with an impressive array of advanced technologies and luxurious amenities, this Optima SX Turbo is the perfect blend of performance and sophistication. Key highlights include:

• SX Turbo Premium Package
• SX Technology Package
• Navigation System
• Infinity Premium Sound System
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Blind Spot Detection with Cross-Traffic Alert
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Outboard Seats
• 4-Way Power Front Passenger Seat
• Rear Camera Display

Powered by a robust 2.0L I4 DGI DOHC Turbocharged engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic with Sportmatic transmission, this Optima SX Turbo delivers an exhilarating driving experience. With a fuel-efficient rating of 20 MPG in the city and 31 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of turbocharged performance without sacrificing efficiency.

Step inside the cabin and you'll be surrounded by a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. The Infinity Premium Sound System with 8 speakers and a subwoofer delivers a truly immersive audio experience, while the SiriusXM satellite radio and HD Radio keep you entertained on every journey. The Panoramic Sunroof floods the interior with natural light, creating a spacious and airy ambiance.

For added convenience and peace of mind, the Optima SX Turbo is equipped with a suite of advanced safety technologies, including Blind Spot Detection with Cross-Traffic Alert and a Rear Camera Display. These features help you navigate busy roads with confidence and ease.

With its striking good looks, exceptional performance, and impressive list of premium amenities, this 2015 Kia Optima SX Turbo is a true standout in the midsize sedan segment. Priced at just $7,290, it represents an exceptional value proposition that is sure to impress.

We invite you to experience the thrill of this remarkable vehicle for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the unparalleled driving experience that the Optima SX Turbo has to offer.

description: FULLY CLEAN CARFAX - 2 FULL REMOTE KEYS - ALL OWNERS MANUALS AND BOOKS - OEM FLOOR MATS - PRIOR CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED BY BMW - FULLY SERVICED For sale is a very nice and very well cared for 2015 BMW 320i in BMW's Black 2 on black leather interior. The car comes well optioned with the highly desired Sport Package. This includes the must have sport bolstered seats, upgraded M sport suspension, larger sport wheels and this one actually has a upgraded M Sport steering wheel. Other high-value options included on this car are Navigation, HiFi speaker system, real-time traffic information, cruise control with braking and more. The car comes with 2 full remote keys, all owners manuals and books and OEM floor mats. This BMW was also a Certified Pre-owned BMW. BMW only chooses the best BMW's to be in this program. This includes mechanical condition, cosmetic condition and any prior accident history. They have the be in the best shape for this program. The car has been very well maintained and it has a fully clean Carfax with 0 accidents, not even a minor accident. We just did all new brakes including rotors on all four corners. We also did the valve cover gasket job required at 100K miles. While we did the valve cover gasket, we also did the eccentric motor and gasket, which is a common failure point on these cars at 100K miles. The valve cover gasket job and the eccentric motor are $4,000+ at the BMW dealership. It also has a brand new oil change and filter using the OEM oil and filters. It also has a brand new windshield installed and calibrated to the vehicle. The car drives the way that it should and it has new errors or warnings on the dash. Raleigh Auto Inc 1302 Capital Blvd 27603 919-821-O952 10am - 5pm Monday - Friday 10am - 2pm Saturday RAI

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2015 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Limited. Boasting a sleek blue exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior, this Legacy is the perfect blend of style and substance.

• Keyless Access & Start
• Power Moonroof Package
• Navigation System
• Aha Infotainment
• harman/kardon Surround Sound Speaker System

Under the hood, you'll find a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT Lineartronic transmission and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. This powertrain delivers an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 36 MPG on the highway, ensuring exceptional efficiency and performance.

The Legacy 2.5i Limited is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of keyless access and start, as well as the panoramic views afforded by the power moonroof. Stay connected and entertained with the state-of-the-art navigation system, Aha infotainment, and premium harman/kardon audio system.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront of this Legacy's design. Sink into the plush, perforated leather-trimmed seats, which offer heating for both the front and rear passengers. The power-adjustable driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel ensure a personalized fit, while the dual-zone automatic climate control keeps everyone comfortable.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like a rear-vision camera, blind-spot monitoring, and a suite of airbags to provide peace of mind on every journey.

Whether you're commuting, embarking on a road trip, or navigating the daily demands of life, this 2015 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Limited is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology by visiting Westgate Kia in Wake Forest, NC, today.

Shop with confidence at Westgate Kia and Westgate Dodge Ram in Wake Forest, NC, your go-to destination for new Kia and Ram vehicles as well as a wide selection of quality pre-owned cars, trucks, and SUVs. Serving Wake Forest, Raleigh, the greater Triangle, and surrounding communities, Westgate delivers trusted service, competitive pricing, and a hassle-free buying experience for every driver in North Carolina.

- Extended Vehicle Service Contract (Warranty),
- Guaranteed Asset Protection (GAP), or
- Other approved ancillary protections.

Representative Payment Example

description:
Discover the epitome of luxury and performance in this stunning 2015 Hyundai Genesis 3.8. Boasting a sleek black exterior and an array of premium features, this all-wheel-drive sedan is the perfect blend of style, technology, and driving dynamics.

Highlights of this exceptional vehicle include:
• Reversible Cargo Tray
• Mud Guards
• First Aid Kit
• Signature Package 02
• Navigation System
• Option Group 02
• Radio: AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM/CD/DVD/MP3 Audio System
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Rear window defroster
• Power Tilt-and-Telescopic Steering Wheel
• Power Tilt-and-Slide Panoramic Sunroof
• Auto-Dimming Outside Mirrors
• HID Headlights w/Auto-Leveling
• Blind Spot Detection System
• Integrated Memory System (IMS)

Powered by a robust 3.8L V6 DGI DOHC Dual CVVT engine, this Genesis delivers an exceptional driving experience with its 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel-drive capability. Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 16 city/25 highway MPG.

The interior of this Genesis is a true sanctuary, featuring premium leather seating, heated and cooled front seats, and a host of advanced technology. The 7-inch TFT LCD cluster display, smart cruise control, and lane departure warning system keep you informed and in control. The panoramic sunroof and Harman Kardon audio system further enhance the driving experience, creating a truly luxurious environment.

Safety is paramount in the Genesis, with features like automatic emergency braking, front and rear parking assistance, and a comprehensive suite of airbags. The blind spot detection system and lane keep assist provide added peace of mind on the road.

This 2015 Hyundai Genesis 3.8 represents an exceptional value, priced at just $9,851. With its remarkable combination of style, performance, and technology, it's an opportunity you won't want to miss. Visit our showroom today and experience the true luxury of the Genesis for yourself.

This Chevrolet includes: EMISSIONS, CALIFORNIA STATE REQUIREMENTS EMISSIONS, CALIFORNIA ULEV125 JET BLACK/JET BLACK, LEATHER-APPOINTED SEAT TRIM Leather Seats HEATHER GRAY METALLIC EMISSIONS OVERRIDE, FEDERAL AUDIO SYSTEM, CHEVROLET MYLINK RADIO WITH NAVIGATION Smart Device Integration Navigation System AM/FM Stereo Bluetooth Connection MP3 Capability ELECTRIC DRIVE 1-Speed A/T A/T ENGINE, RANGE EXTENDER, 1.5L VARIABLE VALVE TIMING, DI, DOHC 4-CYLINDER (STD) 4 Cylinder Engine Plug-In Electric/Gas PREMIER PREFERRED EQUIPMENT GROUP SEATS, FRONT BUCKET WITH RECLINING SEATBACKS AND ADJUSTABLE HEAD RESTRAINTS (STD) Bucket Seats LPO, CARGO NET *Note - For third party subscriptions or services, please contact the dealer for more information.* Start enjoying more time in your new ride and less time at the gas station with this 2017 Chevrolet Volt. This vehicle comes with a navigation system. That doesn't mean you won't get lost. But it does mean you won't stay lost. Added comfort with contemporary style is the leather interior to heighten the quality and craftsmanship for the Chevrolet Volt Premier. More information about the 2017 Chevrolet Volt: The Chevrolet Volt starts at around $33,000 and competes in the mid-sized sedan segment, but it's somewhat unique status as a plug-in hybrid sets the Volt apart from much of the market. With over 50 miles of electric range, it's likely that most owners will get around purely on electric power much of the time they're driving the Volt. However, range anxiety should be non-existent, as the Volt does have a gasoline engine available to recharge the batteries when needed. Chevrolet estimates a total range of about 420 miles if the Volt is not recharged via an external source. Interesting features of this model are excellent smartphone integration, bigger than expected interior, and Extraordinary efficiency without the range anxiety

Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and performance in this exceptional 2017 Toyota Corolla SE. With its sleek exterior, well-appointed interior, and impressive fuel efficiency, this Corolla is the ideal choice for the discerning driver seeking a reliable and versatile sedan.

Highlighted by an impressive array of features, this Corolla SE stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

• Smart Key System with Push-Button Start
• Tilt & Slide Moonroof
• Entune Audio Plus with Connected Navigation
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Heated Power Side Mirrors
• 17-Inch Machined Alloy Wheels

The Corolla's 1.8L I4 DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, achieving up to 35 MPG on the highway. Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, this Corolla will keep you moving with confidence and style.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes both comfort and convenience. Soft-touch materials, supportive front bucket seats, and a host of intuitive technology features create an inviting and user-friendly environment. The Entune Audio Plus system with Connected Navigation seamlessly integrates your smartphone, allowing you to stay connected and entertained on the go.

Designed with safety in mind, the Corolla SE comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Automatic High Beams, Rear Camera, and a suite of airbags to help protect you and your passengers.

This exceptional 2017 Toyota Corolla SE is the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency. With its impressive list of features and exceptional driving dynamics, it's the ideal choice for the modern driver seeking a reliable and versatile sedan. We invite you to experience the Corolla SE for yourself and discover why it's the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description:
Discover the exceptional value and features of this 2017 Kia Forte LX. This well-equipped sedan offers a compelling blend of style, comfort, and efficiency, making it an ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Highlighted features of this Forte LX include:
• LX Popular Package
• 4.3" display audio system with AM/FM/CD/MP3 and SiriusXM
• Bluetooth wireless technology with voice recognition
• Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
• Automatic headlights
• Dual illuminated visor vanity mirrors
• Illuminated ignition and glovebox
• Rear-camera display
• Drive mode system with Normal, ECO, and Sport settings

The Forte's 2.0L I4 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers an impressive 29 MPG in the city and 38 MPG on the highway, ensuring excellent fuel economy for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Forte LX also boasts a sleek, modern exterior in the sought-after Snow White Pearl color. The clean, refined lines and well-proportioned design create a sophisticated appearance that is sure to turn heads.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes comfort and convenience. The premium cloth upholstery, driver's armrest, and other thoughtful touches make every journey a pleasure. The rear-camera display and available driver-assistance technologies further enhance the driving experience, providing added peace of mind.

This 2017 Kia Forte LX represents an exceptional value in the compact sedan segment. With its impressive list of features, efficient powertrain, and stylish design, it's a vehicle that checks all the boxes for the discerning buyer. We invite you to experience the Forte's capabilities firsthand and discover why it could be the perfect fit for your driving needs.

Contact us today to schedule a test drive and let us demonstrate how this Forte LX can elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and quality this vehicle has to offer.

Introducing the stunning 2017 BMW 7 Series 740i, a luxurious and powerful vehicle that will take your driving experience to the next level. This beauty comes equipped with a powerful 3.0L Turbo I6 engine, boasting an impressive 320 horsepower and 330 foot-pounds of torque. Step inside the spacious and elegant interior, designed with the finest materials and cutting-edge technology. The 7 Series 740i offers top-of-the-line features such as a premium sound system, navigation system, and a panoramic sunroof to enhance your driving pleasure.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2017 BMW 7 Series 740i, a true masterpiece in both performance and style. Come see it for yourself and experience the ultimate driving experience today.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology in the 2017 Hyundai Sonata Limited. This exceptional sedan is a true standout, offering a refined and sophisticated driving experience that will captivate you from the moment you lay eyes on it.

Meticulously maintained and expertly detailed, this Sonata Limited boasts an impressive array of features that elevate the driving experience. Highlights include a backup camera, heated and ventilated front seats, a premium Infinity audio system, and a state-of-the-art navigation system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The tech-savvy buyer will appreciate the convenience of the Integrated Memory System, which remembers your preferred settings for the driver's seat and outside mirrors.

• Backup Camera
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Rear Seats
• Integrated Memory System
• Infinity Premium Audio System
• Navigation System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto

Beyond the impressive technology, the Sonata Limited delivers a smooth and responsive ride, thanks to its 2.4L I4 engine and 6-speed automatic transmission with Shiftronic. With an EPA-estimated 25 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, this sedan offers exceptional fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for the daily commute or weekend getaways.

The Sonata's sleek and modern exterior design is complemented by the striking white paint color, which exudes a sense of sophistication and refinement. The HID Xenon headlights and dynamic bending lights not only enhance the vehicle's visual appeal but also provide superior illumination for improved safety and visibility.

Inside, the Sonata's cabin is a true sanctuary, with premium leather seating surfaces, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of convenience features that cater to your every need. The rear sunshades and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure that everyone on board enjoys a comfortable and customized environment.

Whether you're seeking a stylish and practical daily driver or a well-equipped family sedan, the 2017 Hyundai Sonata Limited is an exceptional choice. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that this Sonata will exceed your expectations and become the perfect addition to your lifestyle.

description: 2017 Audi A6 Quattro Premium Plus A sophisticated executive sedan that defines comfort, technology, and timeless German luxury. This A6 comes with a clean title, no accident history, low mileage, and was previously Certified Pre-Owned, reflecting exceptional care and condition. Finished with the S-Line exterior, it presents a sporty yet elegant presence, while driving flawlessly with zero issues, no warning lights, and everything operating exactly as intended. Recently serviced and inspected, it is fully ready for its next owner.Equipped with Audi s legendary Quattro all-wheel-drive system, this A6 delivers confident performance in all conditions. The interior is richly appointed with leather seating and genuine wood trim, offering a true luxury experience. Comfort features include heated front and rear seats with memory, a heated steering wheel, 4-zone climate control, and selectable Comfort/Dynamic driving modes. Technology highlights include keyless entry, push-button start, sunroof, front and rear parking sensors, backup camera, blind-spot monitoring, navigation, Bluetooth, and a BOSE premium sound system.Refined, powerful, and exceptionally well equipped, this Audi A6 represents the highest standard of German engineering and executive-class comfort. (Title transfer and taxes not included.)

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and performance in this 2017 Hyundai Sonata Limited. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive array of advanced features, this sedan is the embodiment of modern driving excellence.

Elevate your commute with the Sonata's impressive list of premium amenities:

• Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB)
• Smart Cruise Control with Start/Stop Capability
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Automatic High Beam Assist
• Electronic Parking Brake
• Rear Parking Assistance System

The Sonata's 2.4L I4 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers a thrilling 185 horsepower, while achieving an exceptional 25 city/35 highway MPG. Whether navigating city streets or cruising the open road, this Hyundai sedan offers a dynamic and efficient driving experience.

Indulge in the Sonata's thoughtfully designed interior, featuring heated and ventilated front seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a premium audio system with navigation. The spacious cabin and generous cargo capacity make this Sonata the perfect companion for your daily adventures or weekend getaways.

Safety is a top priority, and the Sonata is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Blind Spot Monitoring system to the Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

As the flagship of the Hyundai lineup, the Sonata Limited represents the pinnacle of the brand's commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. Discover the joy of owning this exceptional sedan and experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance.

We invite you to visit our showroom and take this 2017 Hyundai Sonata Limited for a test drive. Experience the difference for yourself and let us help you find the perfect vehicle to elevate your driving experience.

Discover the thrilling performance and premium features of this certified pre-owned 2017 Hyundai Elantra Sport. With its turbocharged 1.6L engine, 7-speed dual-clutch transmission, and front-wheel drive, this Elantra Sport delivers an exhilarating driving experience. Step inside and experience the premium comfort and convenience of this Elantra Sport. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob provide a refined touch, while the heated front sport seats keep you cozy on chilly mornings. Enjoy the convenience of Bluetooth hands-free calling and the added peace of mind from the rear-view camera. Whether you're navigating city streets or cruising the highway, this Elantra Sport delivers a driving experience that's both thrilling and practical.

Meticulously maintained and backed by a CARFAX vehicle history report, this Elantra Sport is a true gem. With its sleek white exterior and well-appointed interior, this vehicle is sure to turn heads wherever you go. Upgrade your daily drive with this exceptional Hyundai Elantra Sport.

Imagine the confidence and control you'll feel behind the wheel of this sport-tuned Elantra. The turbocharged engine and responsive dual-clutch transmission provide a dynamic and engaging driving experience, while the sport-tuned suspension and 18-inch alloy wheels enhance the vehicle's agility and handling. Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, this Elantra Sport is ready to deliver an exhilarating and efficient performance.

Elevate your driving experience with the premium features and exceptional value of this certified pre-owned 2017 Hyundai Elantra Sport. Schedule a test drive today and discover the thrill of owning this remarkable vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience with this 2017 Ford Fiesta SE. Boasting a sleek gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this Fiesta is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• 6-Speed Automatic (PowerShift) (3.90 Axle Ratio) (Includes SelectShift)

Powered by a 1.6L I4 Ti-VCT engine and paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, this Fiesta delivers an impressive 27 city/37 highway MPG, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time on the open road.

The Fiesta SE comes equipped with a wealth of features designed to enhance your driving enjoyment and convenience. Enjoy the connectivity of the SYNC Communications & Entertainment System, the comfort of air conditioning, and the added security of a comprehensive safety suite, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control.

Step inside the well-appointed cabin and discover the split folding rear seat, front bucket seats, and front center armrest, providing both style and functionality. The Fiesta's unique cloth upholstery and 15" sparkle silver painted aluminum wheels add a touch of sophistication to this compact package.

Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2017 Ford Fiesta SE is ready to exceed your expectations. Experience the perfect balance of performance, efficiency, and features that will have you eager to get behind the wheel.

Stand out from the crowd with the forward-thinking design and performance of our 2017 Volkswagen Jetta Sport Sedan that pours on the charm! Powered by an impressive Turbo Charged 1.8 Liter 4 Cylinder that offers 170hp while connected to a 6 Speed Automatic transmission with Triptronic and Sport Mode. Inside the masterfully crafted cabin of the Jetta Sport, find everything you need and more with two-tone leatherette seating surfaces, heated front seats, a multi-function steering wheel, pushbutton start and a rearview camera. Staying connected is a breeze thanks VW Car-Net App Connect, Discover Media touchscreen navigation, voice control, and impressive audio with HD radio.

Our Volkswagen Jetta has been engineered to protect you with advanced safety features and has received a 5-Star safety rating. Confidence comes standard with ABS, stability/traction control, a reinforced safety cage construction, advanced airbags, intelligent crash response system, and more! description:
2021 Ram 2500 Laramie

CLEAN CARFAX | 6.7L Cummins Turbo Diesel | 370 HP/850 lb-ft | Laramie 2HH Package

This Ram 2500 Laramie blends legendary Cummins diesel power with refined Laramie comfort. Finished in Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat, it delivers serious towing capability, premium interior features, and proven heavy-duty durability.

Under the hood sits the renowned 6.7L Cummins® I6 Turbo Diesel, producing 370 horsepower and 850 lb-ft of torque, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission and a 3.73 rear axle ratio for confident hauling and trailering.

Performance & Capability

• 6.7L Cummins® Turbo Diesel Engine
• 370 HP/850 lb-ft Torque
• 6-Speed Automatic Transmission
• 3.73 Rear Axle Ratio
• Anti-Spin Rear Differential
• Heavy-Duty Suspension
• Tow Hooks
• Trailer-Ready Platform
• Electronically Controlled Throttle

Built to tow heavy, haul confidently, and handle demanding jobsite conditions.

Premium Laramie Equipment

• Laramie Quick Order Package 2HH
• Leather-Trimmed 40/20/40 Bench Seat
• Heated Front Seats
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Power 8-Way Driver & Passenger Seats
• Power Adjustable Pedals
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Rear 60/40 Folding Seat

Technology & Connectivity

• Uconnect® 4 with 8.4" Touchscreen
• Apple CarPlay® & Android Auto™
• Bluetooth® Connectivity
• Alpine® 9-Speaker Premium Audio with Subwoofer
• SiriusXM® Satellite Radio
• Voice Command
• Steering Wheel Audio Controls

Safety & Driver Assistance

• ParkView® Rear Backup Camera
• Electronic Stability Control
• Brake Assist
• Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS)
• Multiple Airbag System
• Tire Pressure Monitoring

Exterior Highlights

• Chrome Front & Rear Bumpers
• Polished Aluminum 18" Wheels
• Heated Power Mirrors
• Fog Lights
• Rear Step Bumper
• Granite Crystal Metallic Finish

Why This Ram 2500?

The 2021 Ram 2500 Laramie delivers heavy-duty diesel performance with premium comfort and technology. With Cummins torque, Alpine premium audio, leather seating, and proven towing capability, this truck is ready for demanding work while offering the refinement expected from a Laramie trim.

Serious diesel power. Premium interior. Built to perform.

Schedule your test drive today before it’s gone.

description: The 2017 Ford Focus SE is a compact sedan that offers a comfortable ride, efficient performance, and responsive handling. It is powered by a fuel-efficient four-cylinder engine paired with an automatic transmission, providing smooth acceleration well suited for commuting and city driving. The SE trim adds convenience features such as upgraded cloth seating, a touchscreen infotainment system with Bluetooth connectivity, steering-wheel-mounted controls, and keyless entry. The interior is well designed with supportive seating, good visibility, and a quiet ride for its class. Overall, the 2017 Focus SE delivers a practical balance of efficiency, comfort, and driving enjoyment, making it a solid compact sedan choice. This personal vehicle has had two previous owners and stands out for its exceptionally low mileage. With just 44,187 miles reported, it reflects light use and reduced overall wear. The presence of nine service history records indicates routine maintenance and responsible care relative to the mileage. Overall, this vehicle presents as a highly attractive option with low mileage, documented upkeep, and a clean ownership profile supporting strong long-term value. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience with this 2017 Chevrolet Sonic LS. This sleek and modern compact car is ready to take you wherever the road leads, offering a dynamic driving experience and a host of impressive features.

• Local Trade
• Fuel Efficient
• LPO, All-Weather Floor Mats
• License Plate Bracket, Front
• Preferred Equipment Group 1SB

Under the hood, the ECOTEC 1.8L I4 DOHC VVT engine delivers a remarkable balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 24 city/34 highway MPG. Paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, this Sonic LS provides a responsive and enjoyable ride, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising the open highway.

The interior of this Sonic LS is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the intuitive Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a 7-inch touchscreen, seamlessly integrating your smartphone's apps and features. Stay connected with the built-in USB port, while the 4-speaker audio system provides a rich listening experience. Climate control and a rear window defroster ensure you and your passengers stay comfortable, no matter the weather.

Safety is a top priority, and this Sonic LS is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control work together to help protect you and your loved ones. The rear camera provides added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces.

This Sonic LS is a certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. With the added benefits of a comprehensive warranty and 24/7 roadside assistance, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

description: The 2017 Infiniti Q50 2.0T Premium AWD 4-Door Sedan is a luxury sport sedan that melds refined styling, engaging performance, and a premium suite of features into a balanced package. As part of Infiniti’s lineup, the Q50 aims to bridge everyday usability with a touch of athleticism, appealing to drivers who want both comfort and a dynamic driving experience without stepping into full-on performance-car territory. Visually, the 2017 Q50 presents a sleek and modern profile. Its design is characterized by smooth lines, a sculpted hood, and a confident stance enhanced by an aggressive front grille and LED lighting elements. From the side, the flowing roofline and crisp beltline convey a sense of motion even at a standstill. The AWD model adds a planted look, with wider wheel arches and substantial tires that hint at its capability in varied weather conditions. Under the hood, the 2.0T model is powered by a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine. While not as powerful as the larger V6 options in the Q50 lineup, this engine delivers a pleasant balance of responsiveness and efficiency. Turbocharging helps provide brisk acceleration, especially when paired with the sedan’s smooth-shifting automatic transmission. The AWD system contributes to confident traction in rain and light snow, bolstering the car’s all-season usability. Handling is composed, with relatively quick steering and a suspension that absorbs road imperfections well, making the Q50 comfortable on long highway stretches and engaging on winding backroads. Inside, the cabin exemplifies Infiniti’s commitment to luxury. High-quality materials, including soft-touch surfaces and available leather seating, create an upscale atmosphere. The seating is supportive and comfortable, with ample room for front occupants and reasonable space for rear passengers. The trunk offers enough cargo capacity for daily needs and weekend gear, while thoughtful storage solutions help keep essentials organized. Technology is a focal point, with dual touchscreen displays that control infotainment and vehicle settings. Smartphone integration, navigation, and a premium audio system are available, enhancing connectivity and entertainment on the go. The Premium trim includes desirable features such as heated front seats, keyless entry and ignition, and advanced driver-assistance systems. Safety features like forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, lane departure warning, and blind-spot monitoring help elevate confidence behind the wheel. Fuel economy for the 2.0T AWD is competitive within the luxury segment, making the Q50 suitable for both daily commuting and longer journeys. Overall, the 2017 Infiniti Q50 2.0T Premium AWD delivers a compelling blend of performance, luxury, and technology in a refined sedan package.

Full-Size Comfort with Main Character Energy

Meet the 2017 Chevrolet Impala LT 1LT, the sedan that shows up like it pays the mortgage. Big, smooth, and confident, this Impala doesn't just drive--it glides like its late for a very important board meeting where donuts are provided.

Under the hood lives a fuel-friendly yet peppy engine that's perfect for commuting, road trips, or dramatic solo concerts on the way to work. The ride is so comfortable you may accidentally volunteer to drive everywhere just to avoid sitting in your friends car that smells like fries and regret.

Inside, the Impala LT 1LT treats you right: premium cloth seating, power driver seat, dual-zone climate control (because relationships are about compromise), a touchscreen with Bluetooth, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto, plus enough cabin space to make your backseat passengers feel like minor celebrities.

The trunk is enormous--seriously, it could host a small family reunion or at least swallow all the luggage from that we packed light vacation. Safety features, smooth handling, and classic Chevy reliability make this a perfect choice for anyone searching for a dependable full-size sedan without the grandpa car vibes.

If you're shopping for a used 2017 Chevy Impala for sale, a spacious family sedan, or a comfortable commuter car with modern tech, this Impala LT 1LT is ready to upgrade your driveway and your playlist quality.

Powered by a 1.4L 4-Cylinder Turbo DOHC CVVT engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic transmission, the Cruze LS delivers an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG, ensuring exceptional fuel economy for your daily commute or weekend getaways.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that prioritizes both comfort and technology. The Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with a 7-inch touch screen seamlessly integrates with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, providing easy access to your favorite apps, music, and navigation. The Cruze also boasts a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Rear Vision Camera, Traction Control, and Electronic Stability Control, giving you the peace of mind you deserve.

Designed with an eye-catching Silver exterior, the Cruze LS exudes a refined and sophisticated presence on the road. Its sleek lines and sculpted body panels create a dynamic and modern aesthetic that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Versatility is at the heart of the Cruze LS, with ample cargo space and a flexible rear seat that can accommodate your ever-changing needs. Whether you're hauling groceries, transporting sports equipment, or embarking on a road trip, the Cruze has the flexibility to adapt to your lifestyle.

Safety is a top priority in the Cruze LS, with a robust structure and a comprehensive array of airbags, including dual front, side-impact, and overhead airbags, as well as a Knee airbag. The 4-Wheel Disc Brakes and Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS) provide confident stopping power, while the Traction Control and Electronic Stability Control help maintain control in challenging driving conditions.

Experience the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of the 2017 Chevrolet Cruze LS. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this remarkable compact sedan can elevate your driving experience.

Driver Confidence Package ($645 value)
    Preferred Equipment Group 1LT
      Safety and Security
      • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
      • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
      • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
      Technology and Telematics
      • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
      • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

With only 75,921 miles on the odometer, this 2017 Kia Optima EX represents an exceptional value. Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the quality and features of this exceptional midsize sedan.

With its spacious front and rear seating, generous trunk space, and thoughtful comfort touches throughout, the 2017 Taurus SEL offers a balanced blend of practicality and refinement in a traditional sedan package.

description: English description: 2017 Chevrolet Malibu LS — Ecotec 1.5L Turbo I4, 160 hp / 184 lb-ft. This Malibu delivers an efficient and composed driving experience with factory-rated fuel economy of 27 MPG city and 36 MPG highway. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX report, and has had a single owner. Factory-standard features and equipment (stock configuration): - Powertrain and chassis: Ecotec 1.5L turbocharged inline-4 engine producing 160 horsepower and 184 lb-ft of torque, tuned for a balance of performance and fuel economy. Front-wheel drive with factory stability and traction control systems for predictable handling in varied conditions. - Safety: Multiple airbags (front, side-impact, and curtain), anti-lock braking system (ABS), electronic stability control, traction control, and a tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS). Child-seat LATCH anchors are included for rear-seat child restraint installation. - Exterior and convenience: Remote keyless entry, power-adjustable side mirrors, and daytime running lamps. Factory exterior trim and weather sealing designed for everyday use. - Interior and comfort: Cloth seating for five, supportive front seats with manual adjustments, and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat to expand cargo versatility. Manual or automatic climate control depending on factory package, with vents positioned for rear passenger comfort. - Infotainment and connectivity: Chevrolet infotainment system with Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, an AM/FM audio system with auxiliary and USB inputs for device connectivity, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls, and a driver information display that provides trip, fuel economy, and vehicle status information. - Convenience features: Power windows and door locks, cruise control, and ample storage compartments and cupholders throughout the cabin. - Tires and brakes: Factory brakes with ABS and standard all-season tires appropriate for the vehicle’s original specification. This vehicle retains its original factory equipment as described and presents in excellent overall condition. The clean CARFAX and single-owner history add to its appeal for buyers seeking a well-documented, efficiently powered midsize sedan. Spanish translation: Descripción en español: Chevrolet Malibu LS 2017 — Ecotec 1.5L Turbo I4, 160 hp / 184 lb-ft. Este Malibu ofrece una conducción eficiente y equilibrada con un rendimiento de combustible homologado de 27 MPG en ciudad y 36 MPG en carretera. El vehículo se encuentra en excelente estado general, cuenta con un informe CARFAX limpio y ha tenido un solo propietario. Características y equipamiento de fábrica (configuración de serie): - Tren motriz y chasis: motor Ecotec turbo 1.5L de cuatro cilindros en línea que genera 160 caballos de fuerza y 184 lb-ft de torque, ajustado para un equilibrio entre rendimiento y economía de combustible. description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with this 2017 Ford Fusion Hybrid SE. This exceptional vehicle offers a captivating combination of advanced technology, impressive fuel economy, and refined design, making it the ideal choice for the savvy driver seeking a truly exceptional driving experience.

• Power Moonroof
• Universal Garage Door Opener
• Fusion SE Hybrid Appearance Package
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• 18" Premium Painted Dark Stainless Wheels
• Rear Spoiler
• Halogen Fog Lamps
• Navigation System
• Power Driver Seat
• Remote Keyless Entry
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• ABS Brakes
• Dual Front Impact Airbags
• Dual Front Side Impact Airbags
• Emergency Communication System: 911 Assist
• Rear Parking Camera

This Fusion Hybrid SE boasts an impressive 43 MPG in the city and 41 MPG on the highway, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time enjoying the open road. Powered by a robust I4 Hybrid engine paired with an eCVT transmission, this vehicle delivers a seamless and efficient driving experience that will leave you thoroughly impressed.

Beyond its exceptional performance, the Fusion Hybrid SE also showcases a refined and stylish exterior, with a sleek white paint finish that commands attention. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring premium cloth and vinyl seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of advanced technology features, including the SYNC communications and entertainment system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a power moonroof.

Safety is also a top priority, with this Fusion Hybrid SE equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera, ensuring you and your passengers can travel with complete confidence.

Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the daily drive, this 2017 Ford Fusion Hybrid SE is the perfect companion. With its unbeatable combination of efficiency, technology, and style, it's a vehicle that is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today to experience the Fusion Hybrid SE for yourself and discover the true joy of driving.

description: 2017 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S — English description This 2017 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S is powered by a 1.4L turbocharged inline-4 engine that produces 150 hp and 184 lb-ft of torque. The vehicle is front-wheel drive and delivers an EPA-rated fuel economy of approximately 28 MPG city and 38 MPG highway. The car is in excellent overall condition and has a clean CARFAX report. Factory-default features include: - Powertrain and drive: 1.4L turbocharged I4 engine (150 hp / 184 lb-ft), factory transmission options include manual or automatic configurations depending on original equipment. - Exterior: factory-style steel wheels with covers, body-color bumpers and mirrors, halogen headlamps and integrated daytime running lights, and heated rear window defroster. - Interior and comfort: seating for five with durable cloth upholstery, 60/40 split-folding rear seat, manual seat adjustments, air conditioning, tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel, and power windows and door locks. - Infotainment and connectivity: factory audio system with AM/FM radio, auxiliary/USB input and Bluetooth hands-free connectivity for phone and audio streaming, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls. - Convenience: remote keyless entry, cruise control, adjustable mirrors, and a center console with storage and cupholders. - Safety and driver aids: multiple airbags (front, side, and curtain), anti-lock braking system (ABS), electronic stability control, traction control, tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS), and an anti-theft alarm system. Some models originally included a rearview camera as standard or optional equipment depending on the factory package. This Jetta S offers a practical mix of fuel efficiency, everyday comfort, and essential safety features in a well-maintained example with a clean vehicle history. Descripción en español — 2017 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S Este Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S 2017 está equipado con un motor turboalimentado de cuatro cilindros en línea de 1.4L que entrega 150 hp y 184 lb-ft de torque. Es tracción delantera y ofrece un consumo estimado por la EPA de aproximadamente 28 MPG en ciudad y 38 MPG en carretera. El vehículo se encuentra en excelente condición general y cuenta con un informe CARFAX limpio. Características de fábrica (predeterminadas): - Tren motriz y transmisión: motor turbo 1.4L (150 hp / 184 lb-ft), las configuraciones de transmisión de fábrica incluyen opciones manuales o automáticas según el equipo original. - Exterior: ruedas de acero con tapacubos de apariencia de fábrica, parachoques y espejos del color de la carrocería, faros halógenos con luces diurnas integradas y desempañador del vidrio trasero. - Interior y confort: capacidad para cinco pasajeros con tapicería de tela resistente, asiento trasero abatible 60/40, ajustes manuales de asiento, aire acondicionado, volante con ajuste de inclinación y profundidad, y elevalunas y cerraduras eléctricos. - Entretenimiento y conectividad: sistema de audio de fábrica con radio AM/FM, entrada auxiliar/USB y conectividad Bluetooth para llamadas manos libres y reproducción de audio, controles de audio y teléfono en el volante. - Comodidad: entrada remota sin llave, control de crucero, espejos ajustables y consola central con compartimiento y portavasos. - Seguridad y asistencias: múltiples bolsas de aire (frontales, laterales y de cortina), sistema de frenos antibloqueo (ABS), control electrónico de estabilidad, control de tracción, sistema de monitoreo de la presión de los neumáticos (TPMS) y sistema antirrobo. Algunos modelos incluían cámara de reversa de fábrica o como equipo opcional según el paquete original. Este Jetta S representa una combinación práctica de eficiencia de combustible, confort cotidiano y características de seguridad esenciales, en un ejemplar bien cuidado con historial de vehículo description: 2017 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring — English Overview: This 2017 Mazda3 Grand Touring is powered by Mazda’s SKYACTIV-G 2.5L inline-4 engine, rated at 184 hp and 185 lb-ft of torque (PZEV). It delivers an EPA-estimated 27 MPG city and 36 MPG highway. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition and comes with a clean CARFAX report. Factory-installed features: - Powertrain and chassis: SKYACTIV technology including the 2.5L SKYACTIV-G engine and a smooth-shifting transmission (factory-equipped automatic or manual transmission depending on original configuration). Stability and traction control systems and ABS brakes are standard. - Exterior: Upscale exterior touches from the Grand Touring trim, typically including alloy wheels, LED daytime running lights and headlamps, and integrated exterior mirrors with heating and power adjustment. A power sunroof/moonroof is commonly included on this trim. - Interior comfort and convenience: Leather-trimmed seating with heated front seats and power-adjustable driver’s seat. Dual-zone automatic climate control, cruise control, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls, and power windows/locks are all factory-installed conveniences. - Infotainment and connectivity: Mazda Connect infotainment with a center display, integrated navigation on Grand Touring models, Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, HD Radio and satellite radio capability. Premium audio (Bose system on Grand Touring) and steering-wheel/audio interface controls for ease of use. - Keyless and remote features: Keyless entry with push-button start and remote entry are standard on the Grand Touring trim. - Safety and driver assists: A full complement of standard safety features including multiple airbags, ABS, traction control, and a rearview camera. Grand Touring models typically include advanced driver-assist technologies from Mazda’s i-ACTIVSENSE suite such as blind-spot monitoring and rear cross-traffic alert, and often feature lane-departure/mitigation and adaptive cruise control technologies depending on factory options and regional packaging. - Cargo and versatility: Split-folding rear seats to expand cargo capacity, and a well-laid-out cargo area consistent with Mazda3 hatchback or sedan configurations. This vehicle presents as a well-maintained, fully equipped Grand Touring model with strong fuel economy for its class and a clean history report. Specific equipment can vary by market and original factory options, please contact us for the exact build-sheet or VIN-specific factory option list. 2017 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring — Español Resumen: Este Mazda3 Grand Touring 2017 está equipado con el motor SKYACTIV-G 2.5L de 4 cilindros en línea, con 184 hp y 185 lb-ft de torque (PZEV). Equipamiento instalado de fábrica: - Tren motriz y chasis: Tecnología SKYACTIV, que incluye el motor SKYACTIV-G 2.5L y una transmisión de funcionamiento suave (automática o manual según la configuración de fábrica). Frenos ABS y sistemas de control de estabilidad y tracción son estándar. - Exterior: Detalles exteriores de la versión Grand Touring, normalmente con rines de aleación, luces diurnas LED y faros LED, y espejos laterales con calefacción y ajuste eléctrico. Esta versión suele incluir techo solar eléctrico. - Interior, confort y conveniencia: Tapicería en cuero con asientos delanteros calefactables y asiento del conductor con ajuste eléctrico. Control de clima automático de dos zonas, control de crucero, controles de audio y teléfono en el volante, y cristales/pestillos eléctricos como comodidades de fábrica. - Infoentretenimiento y conectividad: Sistema Mazda Connect con pantalla central, navegación integrada en los modelos Grand Touring, conectividad Bluetooth para llamadas y audio, radio HD y capacidad para radio satelital. The XE 35t R-Sport stands as a beacon of design and performance, its Ebony exterior not just a color, but a badge of honor that reflects Jaguar's illustrious racing heritage. Adorned with its sleek aerodynamic body and signature R-Sport styling elements, it presents an assertive stance that demands attention on every drive.


Step inside and the Jet interior with Light Oyster contrast stitching greets you, exuding an air of luxury that only Jaguar can deliver. The R-Sport branded sports seats, precision-crafted materials, and dynamic interior accents underscore the vehicles commitment to elegance and sport-inspired design.

Engine and Performance: At the heart of this refined sport sedan is a 3.0-liter Supercharged V6 engine, delivering a commanding 340 horsepower and 332 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a finely tuned 8-speed automatic transmission, the XE 35t R-Sport delivers swift acceleration and seamless shifts, while its rear-wheel-drive layout ensures pure, engaging performance.

Key Features:

• R-Sport Body Styling: Unique front bumper, side sills, and rear spoiler enhance its aggressive, sporty aesthetic.

• Sport Suspension: Tuned for precision and agility, offering an exhilarating driving experience.

• InControl Touch Navigation: Advanced infotainment system with intuitive navigation and connectivity features.

• Meridian Sound System: Experience exceptional audio clarity with Jaguars premium sound engineering.

• Driver Assistance Features: Including Blind Spot Monitoring, Lane Keep Assist, and Reverse Traffic Detection.

• Interior Mood Lighting: Customize your cabin ambiance with subtle, configurable interior lighting.

This 2017 Jaguar XE 35t R-Sport is far more than just a car, it is the embodiment of the brand's commitment to peak automotive engineering and opulent design. Available at Jaguar Rancho Mirage, this vehicle offers an invitation to experience the thrill of a luxury sports car that pushes the boundaries of excitement and elegance.



Jaguar Rancho Mirage is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful redesigned showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location at 71377 CA-111, Rancho Mirage, CA 92270 We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description: 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D for Sale at American Fleet in Fontana, CaliforniaLooking for a stylish, reliable, and feature-packed sedan? The 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D is here to exceed your expectations. Available now at American Fleet in Fontana, located in San Bernardino, California, this sedan offers a perfect blend of elegance, performance, and advanced technology. Whether you're commuting through the city or embarking on a weekend road trip, the Hyundai Elantra Limited is built to deliver a smooth and enjoyable driving experience. Let s dive into what makes this sedan a standout choice for car buyers in California.Sleek and Sophisticated Design: The 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited SedanThe 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D boasts a sleek and aerodynamic design that catches the eye from every angle. Its bold front grille, sharp headlights, and refined curves make it a head-turner on the road. The addition of alloy wheels enhances its modern appeal while maintaining a sporty edge. Whether you're pulling up to a business meeting or cruising around town, the Elantra Limited's stylish exterior ensures you'll always make a statement.Powerful and Efficient Performance with 6-Speed ShiftronicUnder the hood, the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited is powered by a 2.0-liter 4-cylinder engine that delivers a perfect balance of power and fuel efficiency. Paired with a smooth 6-speed Shiftronic automatic transmission, this front-wheel-drive sedan offers responsive acceleration and effortless handling. Whether you're navigating city streets or hitting the highway, the Elantra Limited ensures a comfortable and confident ride every time.Advanced Safety Features for Peace of MindSafety is a top priority in the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited, and it comes equipped with a suite of advanced safety features to keep you and your passengers protected. The ABS (4-wheel) system, electronic stability control, and traction control work together to provide superior handling and stability in various driving conditions. The blind-spot detection system and backup camera enhance visibility, making lane changes and parking a breeze. Plus, with dual front airbags, front and rear head curtain airbags, side airbags, and knee airbags, you can drive with confidence knowing you're surrounded by a robust safety system.Luxury and Comfort: Interior Features of the 2017 Hyundai Elantra LimitedStep inside the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan, and you'll be greeted by a premium interior designed with your comfort in mind. The plush leather seats offer a touch of luxury, while the heated front seats ensure you stay cozy during cooler mornings. The power-adjustable driver's seat allows you to find your perfect driving position with ease, and the tilt and telescoping steering wheel adds an extra layer of customization. Whether you're running errands or embarking on a long drive, the Elantra Limited's thoughtfully designed interior ensures every journey is a pleasure.Tech-Savvy Features for Modern DriversThe 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited is packed with cutting-edge technology to keep you connected and entertained on the go. The Bluetooth wireless system allows you to make hands-free calls and stream your favorite music effortlessly. The AM/FM stereo and CD/MP3 player provide multiple options for audio entertainment, while the SiriusXM Satellite radio ensures you'll never run out of channels to explore. The Blue Link Telematics system adds another layer of convenience, offering features that enhance your driving experience and keep you in control.Convenience at Your FingertipsThe 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D is designed to make your life easier with a range of convenient features. The keyless entry and keyless start systems allow you to unlock and start the car with minimal effort. The power windows, power door locks, and power steering add to the convenience, while the cruise control feature makes highway driving more relaxed. With the Elantra Limited, every detail is designed to enhance your comfort and simplify your daily routine.Smart Features for a Safer DriveDriving the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited is not just about comfort and style it's also about staying safe on the road. The daytime running lights ensure you're visible to other drivers, while the hill start assist control prevents rollback when you're starting on an incline. These smart features work seamlessly to provide a safer driving experience, making the Elantra Limited a reliable choice for you and your family.Why Buy the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D from American Fleet?At American Fleet, we take pride in offering high-quality vehicles that meet the needs of our customers. The 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D is no exception. Located in the heart of Fontana, San Bernardino, California, our dealership is dedicated to providing a seamless car-buying experience. Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to upgrade your current vehicle, the Elantra Limited is a perfect choice for drivers seeking style, performance, and advanced features in one package.Visit American Fleet in Fontana, California Today!Don't miss your chance to own the 2017 Hyundai Elantra Limited Sedan 4D. Visit American Fleet in Fontana, San Bernardino, California, to see this exceptional sedan in person. Our friendly and knowledgeable team is here to answer your questions and help you find the perfect vehicle to suit your lifestyle. Stop by today and discover why the Hyundai Elantra Limited is the ideal choice for California drivers. Your next adventure starts here!

With its exceptional fuel efficiency, comprehensive list of features, and stylish good looks, this 2010 Nissan Altima 2.5 S is a fantastic value that is sure to impress. Visit our showroom today and experience the Altima for yourself. We're confident you'll be delighted with all it has to offer.
