description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and advanced technology in the 2021 Kia Rio S. This compact sedan offers an exceptional driving experience that caters to the needs of the modern commuter.

Highlighted features include:

• Technology Package: Automatic Temperature Control, Push Button Start, 15" Alloy Wheels, LED Headlights, Forward Collision Avoidance Assist, 8" Rearview Monitor, and more
• 6 Speakers, AM/FM/MP3/SiriusXM Audio System
• Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Rear Occupant Alert
• Supervision Meter Cluster with 4.2" Display

Powered by a 1.6L 4-cylinder engine and equipped with a CVT transmission, the Rio S delivers an impressive 33 city/41 highway MPG, making it a fuel-efficient and cost-effective choice for your daily travels. The front-wheel-drive configuration provides responsive handling and a smooth, comfortable ride.

Beyond its practical attributes, the Rio S boasts a sleek and modern exterior design in a stylish Black color. The LED headlights and positioning lights add a touch of sophistication, while the 15" alloy wheels enhance the vehicle's overall aesthetic appeal.

Step inside the Rio S, and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that prioritizes both form and function. The woven cloth seats provide comfortable support, while the 8" rearview monitor with dynamic parking guidance and rear camera display make maneuvering a breeze. The steering wheel-mounted audio controls and Bluetooth wireless technology allow you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone, keeping you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is also a top priority in the Rio S, with features like Forward Collision Avoidance Assist, Lane Keeping Assist, and Driver Attention Warning working together to help protect you and your passengers. The Highline Tire Pressure Monitoring System and electronic stability control further enhance the vehicle's overall safety and stability.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on weekend adventures, the 2021 Kia Rio S is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect balance of efficiency, technology, and style that this compact sedan has to offer. Visit our showroom today to take the Rio S for a test drive and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.

description: 2021 Honda Accord LX — Crystal Black Pearl exterior / Black premium cloth interior Overview This 2021 Honda Accord LX combines efficient turbocharged performance with a spacious, refined cabin and a long list of factory-installed safety and convenience features. Powered by Honda’s 1.5L Turbocharged inline-4 producing 192 horsepower and 192 lb-ft of torque, the Accord LX delivers a balanced blend of everyday responsiveness and excellent fuel economy — an EPA rating of approximately 30 MPG city and 38 MPG highway. Finished in a deep Crystal Black Pearl exterior with Black premium cloth upholstery, this particular example is in excellent overall condition, carries a clean CARFAX report, and shows a single previous owner. Exterior The Crystal Black Pearl paint presents beautifully on the Accord’s sculpted bodywork. The LX trim features Honda’s clean, aerodynamic design language with crisply defined character lines and a broad stance that projects stability and sophistication. Exterior equipment includes power side mirrors, a handsomely integrated rear trunk spoiler, and clear-lens lighting elements. The front fascia and grille are designed to provide both a modern appearance and improved airflow. Wheels are appropriately scaled to the LX trim, contributing to a comfortable ride and confident handling. Overall exterior condition on this vehicle is excellent, with well-maintained paint and trim showing normal, low-wear use for its model year. Interior and Comfort Step inside to a practical and comfortable cabin trimmed in Black premium cloth. The seating is supportive and designed for long-distance comfort for up to five occupants. Front seats offer good bolstering, and the driver’s position includes an adjustable steering column (tilt and telescoping) for a customized driving posture. Rear passengers benefit from generous legroom and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat that enhances cargo versatility. Interior materials are thoughtfully selected for durability and ease of maintenance, with contrast stitching and tasteful trim accents that elevate perceived quality. Convenience and Storage The Accord LX is equipped with a number of everyday convenience features straight from the factory: power door locks and power windows with one-touch up/down driver window functionality, remote keyless entry, and a multi-function center console with storage cubbies and cupholders. The trunk delivers ample cargo capacity for the class (approximately 16.7 cubic feet), plus easy access via a wide opening and low liftover height — making grocery runs, luggage loading and the occasional bulky item straightforward. Infotainment and Connectivity Factory infotainment equipment provides modern smartphone integration and simple, intuitive controls. The system includes a responsive touchscreen interface with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility to mirror familiar apps and navigation from your phone, as well as Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming. Steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls keep common functions within easy reach, while USB ports provide charging and device connectivity. A multi-angle rearview camera aids in reverse maneuvering and parking. Powertrain and Driving Dynamics Under the hood, the 1.5L Turbo I4 produces 192 hp and 192 lb-ft of torque, routed through a smooth continuously variable automatic transmission (CVT) to the front wheels. The result is a vehicle that feels lively around town and composed on the highway. Acceleration is prompt for daily driving and merging, while the CVT helps maximize fuel efficiency to achieve the posted 30 MPG city / 38 MPG highway figures. The Accord’s suspension tuning delivers a refined ride quality with confident handling — independent suspension components front and rear help isolate road irregularities while maintaining precise steering feel. With its sleek Classic Silver Metallic exterior and a comfortable Ash interior, this sedan presents a balanced mix of modern appeal and understated elegance. With just under 84,000 miles on the odometer, this well-maintained vehicle promises years of reliable service, making it a smart choice for budget-conscious drivers who refuse to compromise on quality. This used Toyota Corolla CE stands out as a practical choice for those valuing longevity and low maintenance costs. Its straightforward design, combined with a spacious four-door body, offers convenience for daily errands and family outings alike. The interior features a comfortable gray upholstery that provides a calm, inviting environment, perfect for long drives or short commutes. Despite its age, the vehicle's condition reflects careful use, and its gasoline engine ensures easy fueling and broad availability of service parts. Whether you're a first-time car buyer or seeking a dependable secondary vehicle, this Corolla's reputation for durability and efficiency makes it a compelling option. With its combination of performance, comfort, and affordability, this sedan is ready to serve your driving needs reliably for years to come.

description:
Discover the ultimate off-road adventure with this stunning 2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. Boasting a powerful 3.0L V6 Turbodiesel engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Wrangler delivers exceptional performance both on and off the beaten path. Equipped with 4-wheel drive, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence, while the impressive fuel efficiency of 22 city and 29 highway MPG ensures you can go the distance.

- **BLUETOOTH**
- **REAR VIEW CAMERA**
- **BLINDSPOT DETECTION**
- **REAR PARK ASSIST**
- **APPLE CARPLAY/ANDROID AUTO**
- 8.4" Touchscreen Display
- GPS Navigation
- Alpine Premium Audio System
- HD Radio
- Rear Window Defroster
- Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection
- ParkSense Rear Park Assist System

This Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is more than just a capable off-road machine – it's a true lifestyle vehicle. The stunning Black exterior is complemented by the premium Black leather-trimmed interior, creating a bold and sophisticated look. The 8.4" Uconnect 4C Nav system with GPS navigation and the premium Alpine audio system ensure you'll enjoy every mile, whether you're tackling the trails or cruising down the highway.

The Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is packed with thoughtful features that elevate your driving experience. The Cold Weather Group includes heated front seats and a heated steering wheel, keeping you comfortable even in the harshest conditions. The LED Lighting Group provides exceptional visibility with premium reflector headlamps, LED fog lights, and LED taillamps. The Trailer Tow & HD Electrical Group equips this Wrangler with a Class II receiver hitch and a 7- and 4-pin wiring harness, making it the perfect companion for your outdoor adventures.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection and the ParkSense Rear Park Assist System keeping you and your passengers secure. The 3-piece Black hard top provides exceptional protection, while the Freedom Panel storage bag ensures you can easily store the removable panels when not in use.

Whether you're tackling the trails, commuting to work, or embarking on a family road trip, this 2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is the ultimate adventure-ready companion. Experience the unparalleled capability, comfort, and style that only a Jeep can deliver. ** FREE CERTIFIED SELECT 12mo/12,000mi WARRANTY ** 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LT - Apple CarPlay/Android Auto - Blind Spot Monitoring - Back-Up Camera - Excellent Condition Inside & Out!

The 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LT delivers modern safety technology, efficient everyday usability, and strong overall value in a well-balanced compact SUV. Ideal for Chicagoland drivers seeking comfort, connectivity, and confidence without excess complexity, this Equinox stands out with low mileage, advanced driver assistance features, and a clean, well-kept interior. Having completed a comprehensive inspection at INFINITI of Clarendon Hills, it offers dependable ownership with added peace of mind.

--
Certified Confidence & Ownership Highlights

~ ** FREE CERTIFIED SELECT WARRANTY 12mo/12,000mi CERTIFED SELECT WARRANTY ** providing added confidence and coverage
~ Strong vehicle history supporting responsible prior ownership
~ Exceptionally low mileage positioning this Equinox well below market averages
~ Completed a thorough 167-point INFINITI of Clarendon Hills inspection
~ Priced competitively for outstanding value in the compact SUV segment

--
Design, Comfort & Everyday Utility

~ Comfortable seating layout designed for daily commuting and longer drives
~ Split-folding rear seats allowing flexible cargo and passenger configurations
~ Clean, functional cabin design focused on ease of use
~ 17-inch aluminum wheels delivering a balanced blend of ride comfort and durability
~ Thoughtful storage solutions supporting everyday errands and travel needs

--
Technology, Connectivity & Convenience

~ Apple CarPlay and Android Auto enabling seamless smartphone integration for calls, navigation, and media
~ Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system providing intuitive touchscreen control
~ Rearview camera improving visibility during parking and reversing
~ Multiple USB ports supporting convenient device charging for front and rear passengers
~ SiriusXM capability expanding entertainment options on longer drives
~ Bluetooth connectivity and steering wheel-mounted controls supporting hands-on operation

--
Safety, Performance & Driving Confidence

~ Predictive forward collision warning supporting proactive awareness
~ Lane Departure Warning and Lane Keep Assist helping maintain lane positioning
~ Blind Spot Monitoring and Rear Cross Traffic Alert assisting in traffic and parking environments
~ Electronic stability and traction control systems promoting confident handling
~ Proven safety engineering earning top industry safety recognition

--
Infinite Rewards Loyalty Program

~ Complimentary Pickup & Delivery Valet Service (if applicable)
~ Courtesy Exterior Car Wash
~ 10% OFF INFINITI Accessories
~ Preferred Loaner Car Status (if applicable)
~ Exclusive DriveSure benefits

description:
Why BUY from Jacobs Motors? When you choose this Nero Ribelle Metallic 2021 Maserati Quattroporte Trofeo with 18,295 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
RED, PIENO FIORE FULL NATURAL LEATHER SEAT UPHOLSTERY Come on in to Jacobs Motors today at 3230 14th St W Bradenton FL 34205 or call to schedule a test drive!

description:
Unleash serious performance with the 2023 Dodge Charger R/T Scat Pack a bold, highoutput sedan that blends exhilarating power with everyday usability. Built for drivers who crave straightline muscle and commanding presence, this Charger variant elevates classic American performance to thrilling new heights.

At the heart of the Scat Pack is a formidable 6.4liter HEMI V8 engine, delivering an impressive burst of horsepower and torque that makes acceleration immediate and addictive. Backed by a performancetuned automatic transmission and launchready drivetrain, the Charger R/T Scat Pack delivers a visceral driving experience thats equally at home on open highways or weekend cruising.

Performanceminded features abound, with beefy Brembo performance brakes, sporttuned suspension, and available performance driving modes that sharpen handling and throttle response. Aggressive exterior styling including a sculpted hood, wide stance, and signature performance cues signals the Chargers serious capability and unmistakable attitude.

Inside, the cabin balances driverfocused ergonomics with supportive comfort. Poweradjustable sport seats, leather trim with performance accents, and a performanceoriented instrument cluster surround you with both style and function. The intuitive infotainment system keeps you connected and entertained with a vivid touchscreen, available premium audio, and seamless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

Safety and confidence are supported with advanced driverassist technologies, helping you stay focused on the drive ahead. From blindspot monitoring to adaptive cruise control, the Charger R/T Scat Pack is designed to blend performance with everyday practicality.

With its commanding power, aggressive styling, and confident handling, the 2023 Dodge Charger R/T Scat Pack delivers an electrifying blend of muscle car heritage and modern performance ready to fuel your passion for the drive.

description:
Look at this 2019 Subaru Forester Premium in Crystal White Pearl with Black interior. This Forester has 106,353 miles. This Subaru Forester comes with a 60 day 3,000 mile safety warranty at no additional cost to you! No Accidents! A copy of the Carfax is always available. This vehicle comes with these options and features Comfort
  • Heated seats offer cool weather comfort by warming the seat quickly, before the air in the passenger compartment is fully warmed by the heater.
Convenience
  • This \'intelligent\' cruise control system uses laser or radar to maintain a preset following distance behind another vehicle, automatically braking (to a complete stop if needed) or accelerating as required.
  • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. The camera is equipped with its own washer.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
  • The vehicle is equipped with sensors which compare vehicle speed to available distance to the vehicle ahead. If the speed exceeds the required distance to stop before colliding with the vehicle ahead, the brakes are automatically readied for maximum braking force once the driver applies the brakes.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
All-Weather Package ($500 value)
  • Heated Front Seats
  • Heated Exterior Mirrors
  • Windshield Wiper De-Icer
Base Model

description:
Discover the exceptional 2019 Audi Q5 2.0T Premium Plus quattro, a remarkable SUV that blends style, performance, and unparalleled luxury. This meticulously maintained, one-owner vehicle is the perfect embodiment of Audi's commitment to engineering excellence.

Boasting a stunning Gray exterior and a host of premium features, this Q5 is ready to elevate your driving experience. Highlights include:

• One Owner Car Fax
• PREMIUM PLUS PACKAGE
• WARM WEATHER PACKAGE
• Wheels: 20" 5-Segment-Spoke Design
• Audi Virtual Cockpit
• Audi Advanced Key
• Driver Seat Memory
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Audi Side Assist
• LED Headlights
• Auto-Dimming Power Folding Mirrors
• Audi Connect PRIME & PLUS
• Audi Phone Box
• Audi Pre Sense Rear
• Front Sport Seats with 4-Way Power Lumbar
• Leatherette Covered Center Console & Door Armrests
• Parking System Plus (Front/Rear Acoustic Sensors)

Under the hood, the 2.0L TFSI engine and 7-Speed Automatic S tronic quattro all-wheel-drive system deliver a thrilling and efficient performance, with an EPA-estimated 22 city/27 highway MPG.

This Q5 is more than just a remarkable vehicle, it's a testament to Audi's commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. From the advanced driver assistance features to the premium cabin materials, every detail has been meticulously designed to provide you with an unparalleled driving experience.

We invite you to experience the exceptional 2019 Audi Q5 2.0T Premium Plus quattro for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true meaning of luxury and performance. We're confident that this remarkable SUV will exceed your expectations and leave a lasting impression.

description: Discover the perfect balance of truck utility and sedan-like efficiency with the 2022 Ford Maverick Lariat. Finished in the popular and distinct Cactus Gray, this compact pickup is powered by the energetic 2.0L EcoBoost Turbocharged engine. Delivering 250 horsepower and 277 lb-ft of torque, this front-wheel-drive Maverick is as peppy as it is practical, achieving a notable 23/30 City/Highway MPG. As a CARFAX One-Owner vehicle, it offers the reliability and "Superior" quality you can depend on.The Lariat trim is the pinnacle of the Maverick lineup, offering a sophisticated interior that stands out from the crowd. You'll find Desert Brown ActiveX Heated Front Seats and a Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel, creating an upscale atmosphere for every journey. The cabin is filled with premium touches like Ambient Lighting, Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, and an Acoustic Windshield that significantly reduces road noise. For added convenience, the Intelligent Access with Push-Button Start ensures you never have to fumble for your keys.Utility is built into the Mavericks DNA with the innovative FLEXBED system. The 4.5-foot bed is designed for DIY flexibility, featuring built-in slots for 2x4s and 2x6s, allowing you to create custom racks or segmented storage. With a 1,500-lb payload capacity and a Power Locking Tailgate, this truck is ready for weekend projects or cross-town escapes. Inside, you'll also find clever storage solutions like Rear Under-Seat Storage Bins to keep your gear organized and out of sight.Safety and technology are seamlessly integrated through the Ford Co-Pilot360 suite. You'll drive with total confidence thanks to BLIS (Blind Spot Information System) with Cross-Traffic Alert, a Lane-Keeping System, and Pre-Collision Assist with Automatic Emergency Braking. Staying connected is effortless with the 8-inch Touchscreen featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, while the 6.5-inch Productivity Screen in the instrument cluster keeps vital vehicle information right in your line of sight.The 2022 Ford Maverick Lariat is a modern tool for the modern driver compact enough for easy city parking, but tough enough to handle your outdoor lifestyle. From its Auto High-beam Headlights to its Remote Keyless Entry, every feature is designed to make your daily drive simpler and more enjoyable. Visit us today to see how this "Superior" Maverick can fit perfectly into your life.Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

The 2021 Frontier is a unique bridge model. While it retains the classic, rugged body style that truck owners love, it features the all-new powertrain (engine and transmission) that was later used in the fully redesigned 2022+ models. 2021 Nissan Frontier S Crew Cab Proven Grit, Modern Heart Get the best of both worlds with this 2021 Nissan Frontier S . This classic body style is legendary for its durability and built-like-a-tank reputation, but don't let the exterior fool youunder the hood lies a modern, powerful heart. Featuring the advanced 3.8L V6 engine introduced just a year prior, this truck offers more standard horsepower than nearly any other midsize pickup in its class. The Heart of the Next Frontier The 2021 model was the first to fully integrate Nissans latest powertrain technology: Best-in-Class Horsepower: The 3.8L Direct Injection V6 produces a massive 310 horsepower , providing effortless merging and heavy-duty hauling capability. 9-Speed Automatic Transmission: Replacing the old 5-speed, this smooth-shifting 9-speed optimizes gear ratios for better acceleration and improved highway fuel efficiency. Push-Button Start: A modern convenience that comes standard, along with a revised center console for the 2021 model year. Rugged Capability The Frontier S is designed to work. Built on a full-length, fully boxed ladder frame using high-tensile strength steel, its engineered for serious tasks: Towing Power: When properly equipped, this Crew Cab 4x2 can tow up to 6,620 lbs , perfect for trailers, boats, or weekend toys. Maneuverability: Its midsize dimensions make it far easier to park and navigate in urban environments than a full-size pickup. Utility: The Crew Cab configuration provides four full-sized doors, ensuring your crew or family rides in comfort with plenty of interior storage. Technical Specifications: 2021 Nissan Frontier S Mechanical & Performance Engine: 3.8L Direct Injection Gasoline (DIG) DOHC 24-valve V6 Horsepower: 310 hp @ 6,400 RPM Torque: 281 lb-ft @ 4,400 RPM Transmission: 9-speed Automatic Drivetrain: Rear-Wheel Drive (4x2) Suspension: Independent double-wishbone front/Overslung multi-leaf rear solid axle Fuel Economy & Capacities EPA Mileage (Est): 18 City/24 Highway/20 Combined MPG Fuel Tank Capacity: 21.1 Gallons Maximum Towing: 6,620 lbs Maximum Payload: Approx. 1,460 lbs Bed Length: 59.5 inches (Standard Bed) Standard Features & Safety Technology: 7.0-inch color touchscreen display, Bluetooth Hands-free Phone System, and Siri Eyes Free. Interior: Cloth bucket seats, 2nd-row under-seat storage, and power windows/locks. Safety: RearView Monitor (Backup Camera), Zone Body construction with front/rear crumple zones, and Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). Dealer Note: This is the ideal truck for the buyer who wants the bulletproof reliability of the classic Frontier frame but wants the performance and efficiency of a modern 2020s drivetrain. It is arguably the most reliable version of the Frontier ever built.

Coupled with Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, this SUV is ready to tackle any terrain with confidence and capability.

Subaru Certified Pre-Owned vehicles undergo a rigorous 152-point inspection, ensuring you can purchase with peace of mind. Along with a Roadside Assistance program, a $0 deductible Transferable Warranty, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty extending up to 84 months/100,000 miles, this Forester Wilderness is a true standout in the pre-owned market.

Elevate your driving experience and embrace the great outdoors with the 2024 Subaru Forester Wilderness. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of ruggedness and refinement that will transform the way you explore the world around you.

Highlighted features include:
• HIGH WALL ALL-WEATHER FLOOR MATS

Powered by Mazda's renowned SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, the CX-30 delivers a thrilling yet efficient performance, with an impressive 24 city/31 highway MPG. The available all-wheel-drive system ensures confident control in any driving condition, making this vehicle the perfect companion for your adventures.

Step inside the CX-30 and be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium leather seating, heated front seats, and a power moonroof. The MAZDA CONNECT™ Infotainment System keeps you connected and entertained, with seamless integration of your favorite smartphone apps through Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™.

Safety is paramount in the CX-30, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Smart City Brake Support. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Designed to turn heads, the CX-30 2.5 S Carbon Edition boasts a striking exterior with bold 18-inch black alloy wheels, a sporty rear spoiler, and distinctive Carbon Edition accents. This vehicle is a true testament to Mazda's commitment to crafting vehicles that blend exceptional performance, premium amenities, and head-turning style.

Experience the difference with the 2022 Mazda CX-30 2.5 S Carbon Edition. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this remarkable crossover SUV should be your next automotive companion. With a starting price of $23,991, the CX-30 offers unbeatable value and an exceptional driving experience that will exceed your expectations.

description: Experience the 2024 Mitsubishi Outlander SE: Where Style Meets Safety and Performance for the Modern Adventurer Discover the perfect blend of style, safety, and performance with the 2024 Mitsubishi Outlander SE. This used, yet impeccably maintained, Alloy Silver Metallic SUV is designed for those who crave adventure without compromising on comfort or security. Its 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC engine ensures a smooth and efficient ride, while the CVT transmission offers seamless gear shifts for an exhilarating driving experience. Safety is paramount in the Outlander, featuring a comprehensive suite of advanced technologies like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Departure Warning, and Rear Collision Mitigation. These features provide peace of mind, whether you re navigating busy city streets or exploring off-the-beaten-path destinations. The adaptive cruise control and aerial view display system make long drives more enjoyable and stress-free. Inside, the Outlander SE boasts a spacious interior with a 3rd-row seat, premium synthetic materials, and heated front seats, ensuring comfort for all passengers. The power liftgate and keyless start add convenience to your daily routine, while the navigation system and smart device integration keep you connected on the go. Embrace the journey with the 2024 Mitsubishi Outlander SE, where every drive is an adventure waiting to happen. Be sure to call or visit Infiniti on Camelback to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

With its rugged good looks and spacious, well-appointed interior, this Tacoma SR5 is the perfect blend of utility and comfort. The white exterior paint gives it a clean, modern appearance, while the 17-inch alloy wheels and chrome accents add a touch of style.

Inside, you'll find a host of premium features, including an 8-inch Toyota Audio Multimedia system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, a rearview camera, and a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies like automatic high beams, lane departure warning, and forward collision mitigation.

Whether you're hauling gear for your next outdoor adventure or simply commuting in comfort, this 2024 Toyota Tacoma SR5 is up for the task. With its proven reliability, versatile capabilities, and impressive list of features, it's an excellent choice for anyone in the market for a capable and well-equipped mid-size pickup.

description:
Theres a startling sort of calm to the 2021 Porsche Taycan Base the kind of presence that doesnt shout so much as rearrange expectations. From afar it reads like a familiar silhouette remade for the future: taut hips and a low, deliberate nose that recall Porsche lineage, but the details are translated into an electric tautness. The profile is elegant rather than aggressive, a study in proportions that suggest speed even at rest, the effect is quietly provocative, promising performance delivered with clarity rather than bluster.

Slide inside and the Taycan greets you with a cockpit that feels both minimalist and meticulously considered. Surfaces are sculpted to meet the hand, materials chosen for tactile satisfaction: soft leathers, variant trims that feel purposeful, and switchgear with satisfying resistance. The drivers seat becomes a stage the console, a concise instrument cluster of screens and touchpoints that prioritize focus. Technology is present but disciplined, it assists rather than overwhelms, keeping the sensory world of road, wheel and tire at the center of the experience.

On the road the Taycans argument is subtle and persuasive. Theres an immediate, almost invisible shove that defines electric propulsion: acceleration arrives with blunt efficiency and near-surgical poise, surging forward without the mechanical drama of an internal combustion engine. The cars low center of gravity and balanced chassis make cornering feel surgical and confident, steering is crisp and communicative, encouraging precise placement and rewarding commitment. Regenerative braking becomes another tool of expression rather than an afterthought, allowing a rhythm of single-pedal control that feels modern and satisfying.

Acoustically, the Taycan plays a different game. Silence is part of the charm, punctuated by a composed mechanical whirr and the tasteful augmentation of sound when one desires drama. The result is intimacy a cabin where conversation and music exist alongside kinetic intensity.

Practicalities arent ignored: luggage space and everyday ergonomics are thoughtfully integrated, letting the Taycan double as both a daily companion and an occasional provocateur. In short, the 2021 Taycan Base is a refined electric athlete restrained, incisive and emotionally calibrated for drivers who appreciate performance served with intellectual elegance.
